1. *Adame*, da li si video moju knjigu? (Hey man, have you seen my book?)
2. Kupio sam *adame* pet kilograma jabuka. (I bought five kilograms of apples, man.)
3. Čujem da je *adame* došao novi profesor u školu. (I heard that a new teacher came to school, man.)
4. Nisam mogao da se koncentrišem jer su *adame* deca galamila. (I couldn't concentrate because the kids were making noise, man.)
5. *Adame*, jesi li čuo vesti o tom novom restoranu? (Hey man, have you heard the news about that new restaurant?)
6. U parku su se igrala deca, a *adame* su roditelji sedeli na klupama. (Children were playing in the park, and the parents were sitting on the benches, man.)
7. Prošle nedelje sam bio na rođendanu kod *adame* Milana. (I was at Milan's birthday party last week, man.)
8. *Adame*, jesi li ti siguran da si zaključao vrata? (Hey man, are you sure you locked the door?)
9. Vidim da *adame* imaju veliku količinu posla, možda im treba pomoć. (I see that they have a lot of work, man, maybe they need help.)
10. *Adame*, sviđa mi se tvoja majica, gde si je kupio? (Hey man, I like your shirt, where did you buy it?)